title: Memphis Zoo's oldest Giraffe, Marilyn, dies at 26
abstract: MEMPHIS, Tenn. (AP)   Memphis Zoo officials have announced that its oldest giraffe has died at 26. The Commercial Appeal reports Marilyn came to the zoo in 2002 and gave birth to six calves throughout her time there. Those calves also later had babies of their own. Zoo officials...

title: Driver arrested after Jeep crashes into water at Sarasota Bayfront
abstract: A driver who drove their Jeep into the water near Sarasota's Bayfront has been arrested. It happened Tuesday evening on 10th Street, according to the Sarasota Police Department.
